{
  "chapterId": "01",
  "title": "第1章 Spring Boot 整体概述",
  "sections": [
    {
      "sectionAnchor": "11-spring-framework-的核心特性",
      "questions": [
        {
          "id": "01-001",
          "type": "single",
          "difficulty": "easy",
          "question": "Spring Framework 的两大核心特性是？",
          "options": [
            { "id": "A", "text": "IOC 与 AOP" },
            { "id": "B", "text": "JDBC 与 ORM" },
            { "id": "C", "text": "MVC 与 WebFlux" },
            { "id": "D", "text": "事务 与 安全" }
          ],
          "correctAnswer": ["A"],
          "explanation": "IOC（控制反转）负责对象的创建与依赖管理，AOP（面向切面编程）负责横切关注点的解耦，两者共同构成 Spring 的核心。",
          "referenceAnchor": "11-spring-framework-的核心特性"
        },
        {
          "id": "01-004",
          "type": "single",
          "difficulty": "medium",
          "question": "Spring Framework 中 IOC 思想最直接的体现是？",
          "options": [
            { "id": "A", "text": "由调用方主动 new 对象" },
            { "id": "B", "text": "对象由 Spring 容器创建并注入到使用者手中" },
            { "id": "C", "text": "所有 Bean 必须是单例" },
            { "id": "D", "text": "通过反射调用方法" }
          ],
          "correctAnswer": ["B"],
          "explanation": "IOC（Inversion of Control）把对象的创建与依赖管理从业务代码中剥离，交给 Spring 容器；调用方只声明需要什么（DI），容器负责装配。这是与主动 new 的根本区别。",
          "referenceAnchor": "11-spring-framework-的核心特性"
        },
        {
          "id": "01-005",
          "type": "single",
          "difficulty": "medium",
          "question": "Spring AOP 主要解决哪类问题？",
          "options": [
            { "id": "A", "text": "数据库连接管理" },
            { "id": "B", "text": "横切关注点（logging / tx / security）的解耦" },
            { "id": "C", "text": "REST 接口定义" },
            { "id": "D", "text": "Bean 作用域" }
          ],
          "correctAnswer": ["B"],
          "explanation": "AOP 把分散在多个方法中的横切逻辑（日志、事务、安全）抽离成切面，避免代码重复。它是 OOP 的补充而非替代。",
          "referenceAnchor": "11-spring-framework-的核心特性"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sectionAnchor": "12-spring-boot-的核心特性",
      "questions": [
        {
          "id": "01-002",
          "type": "multiple",
          "difficulty": "medium",
          "question": "下列哪些是 Spring Boot 的核心特性？（多选）",
          "options": [
            { "id": "A", "text": "约定大于配置" },
            { "id": "B", "text": "自动装配" },
            { "id": "C", "text": "嵌入式 Web 容器" },
            { "id": "D", "text": "强制使用 Maven 构建" }
          ],
          "correctAnswer": ["A", "B", "C"],
          "explanation": "Spring Boot 的四大核心特性是：约定大于配置、自动装配、嵌入式 Web 容器、生产级特性（健康检查/监控）。它对构建工具没有强制要求。",
          "referenceAnchor": "12-spring-boot-的核心特性"
        },
        {
          "id": "01-006",
          "type": "single",
          "difficulty": "medium",
          "question": "Spring Boot 中\"约定大于配置\"最典型的体现是？",
          "options": [
            { "id": "A", "text": "必须为每个 Bean 写 XML 配置" },
            { "id": "B", "text": "组件放在约定路径下即可被自动扫描注册" },
            { "id": "C", "text": "所有类必须实现某个接口" },
            { "id": "D", "text": "禁止使用注解" }
          ],
          "correctAnswer": ["B"],
          "explanation": "约定大于配置：主类放在根包下、Controller 放在 controller 包下、配置文件叫 application.yml 即可生效——无需显式声明扫描路径。",
          "referenceAnchor": "12-spring-boot-的核心特性"
        },
        {
          "id": "01-007",
          "type": "single",
          "difficulty": "easy",
          "question": "Spring Boot 启动后默认开启的嵌入式 Web 容器是？",
          "options": [
            { "id": "A", "text": "Jetty" },
            { "id": "B", "text": "Undertow" },
            { "id": "C", "text": "Tomcat" },
            { "id": "D", "text": "Netty" }
          ],
          "correctAnswer": ["C"],
          "explanation": "spring-boot-starter-web 默认引入 spring-boot-starter-tomcat，Tomcat 是 Spring Boot 的默认嵌入式 Servlet 容器。",
          "referenceAnchor": "12-spring-boot-的核心特性"
        },
        {
          "id": "01-008",
          "type": "multiple",
          "difficulty": "medium",
          "question": "Spring Boot 的\"生产级特性\"通常通过哪个模块提供？（多选）",
          "options": [
            { "id": "A", "text": "spring-boot-starter-actuator" },
            { "id": "B", "text": "健康检查 /health" },
            { "id": "C", "text": "指标收集 /actuator/metrics" },
            { "id": "D", "text": "编译时注解处理" }
          ],
          "correctAnswer": ["A", "B", "C"],
          "explanation": "spring-boot-starter-actuator 提供健康检查、指标、审计、HTTP 跟踪等生产级能力；编译时注解处理与生产运维无关。",
          "referenceAnchor": "12-spring-boot-的核心特性"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sectionAnchor": "13-快速创建第一个-spring-boot-项目",
      "questions": [
        {
          "id": "01-003",
          "type": "single",
          "difficulty": "easy",
          "question": "Spring Boot 项目的主类通常使用哪个注解标记？",
          "options": [
            { "id": "A", "text": "@SpringBootApplication" },
            { "id": "B", "text": "@Component" },
            { "id": "C", "text": "@RestController" },
            { "id": "D", "text": "@Configuration" }
          ],
          "correctAnswer": ["A"],
          "explanation": "@SpringBootApplication 是组合注解，包含 @SpringBootConfiguration、@EnableAutoConfiguration、@ComponentScan，是 Spring Boot 应用的启动入口标识。",
          "referenceAnchor": "13-快速创建第一个-spring-boot-项目"
        },
        {
          "id": "01-009",
          "type": "single",
          "difficulty": "medium",
          "question": "@SpringBootApplication 等价于下列哪一组组合注解？",
          "options": [
            { "id": "A", "text": "@Component + @Service + @Repository" },
            { "id": "B", "text": "@SpringBootConfiguration + @EnableAutoConfiguration + @ComponentScan" },
            { "id": "C", "text": "@Configuration + @Import + @Conditional" },
            { "id": "D", "text": "@EnableAutoConfiguration + @ComponentScan" }
          ],
          "correctAnswer": ["B"],
          "explanation": "@SpringBootApplication 内部由这三个元注解组合：@SpringBootConfiguration（配置类）、@EnableAutoConfiguration（开启自动装配）、@ComponentScan（组件扫描）。",
          "referenceAnchor": "13-快速创建第一个-spring-boot-项目"
        },
        {
          "id": "01-010",
          "type": "single",
          "difficulty": "easy",
          "question": "Spring Boot 应用最常见的启动入口方法是？",
          "options": [
            { "id": "A", "text": "public void main(String[] args)" },
            { "id": "B", "text": "public static void main(String[] args)" },
            { "id": "C", "text": "public int run(String[] args)" },
            { "id": "D", "text": "public static ApplicationContext run()" }
          ],
          "correctAnswer": ["B"],
          "explanation": "Spring Boot 入口方法固定为 public static void main(String[] args)，内部调用 SpringApplication.run() 启动容器。",
          "referenceAnchor": "13-快速创建第一个-spring-boot-项目"
        },
        {
          "id": "01-011",
          "type": "single",
          "difficulty": "easy",
          "question": "Spring Initializr 的作用是？",
          "options": [
            { "id": "A", "text": "运行 Spring Boot 应用" },
            { "id": "B", "text": "在线 / IDE 插件快速生成 Spring Boot 项目骨架" },
            { "id": "C", "text": "Spring Boot 的部署工具" },
            { "id": "D", "text": "Spring 官方论坛" }
          ],
          "correctAnswer": ["B"],
          "explanation": "Spring Initializr（start.spring.io 或 IDE 内置）让用户通过 Web 表单 / IDE 插件选择依赖与 Java 版本，一键生成 Maven/Gradle 项目骨架。",
          "referenceAnchor": "13-快速创建第一个-spring-boot-项目"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
